skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Listen to weekly updates from your favorite source, the Flat Rock Times. We are a local grassroots news company growing everyday to keep you up to date on The City of Flat Rock. You can just say "Alexa, what's my flash briefing". You can say "Alexa, stop" to exit anytime.
